@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram for E Visa Processing And Follow Up System

[*] --> AccountCreation

state "Account Creation" as AccountCreation
AccountCreation : entry / Create account
AccountCreation : do / Verify details
AccountCreation : exit / Account created or not

AccountCreation --> [*] : [Invalid Details]
AccountCreation --> Login : [Valid Details]

state Login
Login : entry / Log in
Login : do / Verify password
Login : exit / Logged in or not

Login --> [*] : [Improper Password]
Login --> VisaApplication : [Proper Password]

state "Visa Application" as VisaApplication
VisaApplication : entry / Apply for visa after login, make payment
VisaApplication : do / Accept application
VisaApplication : exit / Application accepted or not

VisaApplication --> ViewStatus : [View status]
VisaApplication --> CancelApplication : [Cancel application]

state "View Status" as ViewStatus
ViewStatus : entry / Check the status
ViewStatus : do / Update status based on document check
ViewStatus : exit / Status updated or not

ViewStatus --> [*] : [No Change in Status]
ViewStatus --> ModifyDetails : [Modify details after viewing status]

state "Modify Details" as ModifyDetails
ModifyDetails : entry / Update user's details
ModifyDetails : do / Update details
ModifyDetails : exit / Details updated or not

ModifyDetails --> ViewDetails : [View details]
ModifyDetails --> GiveFeedback : [Give feedback after modifying details]

state "View Details" as ViewDetails
ViewDetails : entry / View personal information
ViewDetails : do / Show user's details
ViewDetails : exit / Exit view details page

ViewDetails --> [*] : [No Change in Details]
ViewDetails --> ModifyDetails : [Modify more details]

state "Give Feedback" as GiveFeedback
GiveFeedback : entry / Provide feedback after checking status
GiveFeedback : do / Add feedback
GiveFeedback : exit / Feedback given or not

GiveFeedback --> [*] : [No Feedback Given]
GiveFeedback --> ViewStatus : [Check status again after giving feedback]

state CancelApplication
CancelApplication : entry / Cancel the application
CancelApplication : do / Cancel application
CancelApplication : exit / Application cancelled or not

CancelApplication --> Login : [Logged out after cancellation]

state "Logout" as Logout
Logout : entry / Log out
Logout : do / End session
Logout : exit / User logged out

Login --> ViewDetails : [View details]
Login --> VisaApplication : [Apply for visa and make payment]
Login --> ModifyDetails : [Modify user's details]
Login --> GiveFeedback : [Give feedback after checking status]

@enduml
